cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it."
title: "Memorised them All"
abstract: >-
  Local, token-free file-to-knowledge-graph memory MCP server and plugin for
  Claude (Desktop and Code). Converts PDFs, Office documents, images, and audio
  to Markdown entirely on-device, then builds a layered knowledge graph,
  exportable Markdown memory, and an offline interactive mind map using local
  models — costing near-zero context tokens to build or recall.
type: software
